5064 - Electrical Appliances, Television and Radio Sets Summary > WAHL AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover electrical appliances, television and radio sets. The company is involved in the import and export of goods. WAHL AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Acacia Ridge, Queensland. It is headed by director & company secretary George Gordon Davie. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of $37.69 million. Its net profit totalled $5.33 million. WAHL AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the wholesale trade industry sector.
